{% extends '_templates/base.njk' %}

{% block page_title %}Welcome to Greatreads{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6">
      <h2 class="fw-bold">Welcome to Bituin Books</h2>
      <p>"Bituin," meaning "star" in Filipino, could be seen as the guideâ€”a constellation that helps illuminate the crossroads of who you are and who you are becoming, one book, one life at a time. The idea becomes more than just reading; it becomes living. Each book is a life you take on, like an alternate dimension of yourself, each illuminating new ways to exist, think, and feel.</p>

      <h2>Book Reviews</h2>
      <div id="reviewCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        {% for entry in reviews.posts %}
            <li data-target="#reviewCarousel1" data-slide-to="{{ loop.index0 }}">
            {% if loop.first %}class="active"{% endif %}
            </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>

    <!-- Carousel Inner Slides -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            {% for entry in reviews.posts %}
                <div class="carousel-item {% if loop.first %}active{% endif %}">
                    <a href="blog/{{ entry.slug }}.html">
                        <img src="../img/{{ entry.image }}" class="d-block w-50 mx-auto">
                    </a>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
        </div>

    <!-- Carousel Controls -->
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#reviewCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#reviewCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>

    </div>
{% endblock %}